            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div id="main">
      
    

<div data-post-date-group="" data-post-info="">
      <p><span>Published:</span>
        <time datetime="2026-06-24T08:35:02">June 24, 2026, 8:35 pm</time>
      </p>
        <p><i role="presentation">
  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M6 6v6a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h10l-4 -4m0 8l4 -4"></path></svg>
</i>          <span>Last updated:</span>
          <time datetime="2026-06-24T08:46:34">June 24, 2026, 8:46 pm</time>
        </p>
    </div>
    <article>
      <p>If you're reading this post then you already know you can read our work on this website, the place our blogs feel most at home, but did you know you can also follow us on a load of <em>other </em>sites?</p><p>Some of them are great ways to keep up with whenever we're posting new stories in real time, some are home to clips and highlights from our podcast and video work, while others--like Linkedin--we're not really sure what we're doing there. Luke<a href="https://aftermath.site/linkedin-weird-guy-video-games/"> <u>likes to hang out there and bully tech weirdos</u></a>, but we don't even know if we're reaching any new readers there or not.</p><p>Here's a complete list of all our social media sites. We'd love it if you could follow us at any that you're currently using/doomscrolling through!</p><ul><li><a href="https://bsky.app/profile/aftermath.site?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Bluesky</a></li><li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/aftermathdotsite/?hl=en&amp;ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Instagram</a></li><li><a href="https://youtube.com/@aftermath_site?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">YouTube</a></li><li><a href="https://www.twitch.tv/aftermathdotsite/clips?range=all&amp;ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Twitch</a></li><li><a href="https://x.com/Aftermath_site?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Twitter</a></li><li><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@aftermath_site?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Tik-Tok</a></li><li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/aftermathsite?ref=aftermath.site" rel="noreferrer">Linkedin</a></li><li>Fediverse / Mastodon (@index@aftermath.site)</li></ul><p>Of course, if you'd rather just follow us here and press F5 all day, that's great too! if that's you, you should also know (if you don't already) <a href="https://aftermath.site/latest/" rel="noreferrer">that we've got a special 'latest story mode' just for you</a>. </p>
    </article>

        

      

          

        

